Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你聽說有龍在大鬧了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在哪裡 倫敦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說有個女孩把發瘋的龍馴服了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是哪個女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是能和我們交流的夜之愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個就麻煩你處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 還有要給托利的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會貼上標籤 就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能是那之後就沒好好睡過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來不是沒問題 你需要點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一大碗馬鈴薯泥 還有滿滿的培根
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}食堂有韭蔥湯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬克杯倒滿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後要做什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}決定歸還龍的日子 溝通好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你很疲倦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是師父的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}林德爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 把你呼來喚去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這也沒辦法 你不能離開那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直到找到下位管理人 或者龍徹底滅絕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是個善良的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在那裡只是適應不了新時代而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別垂頭喪氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有什麼錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒有成為魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本來想幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是個半吊子的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是這點雜務都沒辦法輕鬆搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就不能留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}累壞變成小孩子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是 無論那個紅髮女孩還是這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有討厭的事逃掉或者忘掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然特地自討苦吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這件事 真是活多久都想不透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剩下就是睡覺 這樣就夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}邀請函上這麼寫 就照著做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在就相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瑪莉艾爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎兩位年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是菲莉絲 是這個集會的祭司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}差不多就是個主持吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個人長著根
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感謝您的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我聽瑪莉艾爾說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們在尋找同時讓龍活著又能解咒的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我們在場者都不知道這種方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}菲莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瑪莉艾爾 你的意思我心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們無法實現他們的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就沒理由請他們幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要我們幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想封印自己被固定在這棵樹上的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瑪莉艾爾想用你擁有的龍之力救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用在意 人早晚會回歸麈土
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你現在先擔心自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要救人得先救自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經活得夠久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這副模樣也算是個證明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}證明自己還是能幫上別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也有人不值得救
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我們無從知曉未來發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要走哪條路 怎麼走 都是人的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說不定救下的人 將來還能解除別人的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:08:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這裡等待這份快樂可是我的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我認識的人說過類似的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有志同道合的同伴 真叫人高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要龍還活著 在不考慮殺死它的前提下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}詛咒就無法解除 也無法收回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼理解沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我等的見解就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常抱歉 勞煩你們來此一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會 感謝您讓我們參加此次集會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}荊棘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是賠禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能選擇一方肯定很艱難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然沒有收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是繼續加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去幫忙準備早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要換回一條命 必須付出另一條命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 無論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你都會選擇智世吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在那裡吧 風之民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是個良宵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把你觀風聞風的能力借我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想吃多少都行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真大方 我並不討厭你的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩滋華斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}賽門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你來得剛好 我正準備把這些送給智世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遇到什麼開心事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼這麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看起來精神奕奕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就好像有了目標一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前的你 在我看著的這十年裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總是都心不在焉似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這或許是我第一次強烈想去完成一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我正準備去你那裡玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}省得我花時間找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七朵 八朵 何處開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}孩兒沉睡在美夢裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽送給你一束花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽送給你一束花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好重的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空氣精靈 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個醜陋的身體是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是你當初跟我走 就不會變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很快就能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你現在好像蛻皮新生了一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是試著積極一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空氣精靈 如果我不是夜之愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就不會這樣在意我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯在盤算著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且是瞞著我 一個人去做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明說好我們一起想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說不定路茲也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我希望有個不管發生什麼事 都能聽我話的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果不是喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而是喜歡夜之愛子這個身份的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就不會站在艾利亞斯他們那邊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這話雖然沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我也喜歡你啊 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝 那這件工作就不麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道你要找別人說一樣的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你打算做什麼 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世已經快撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們要是不想失去她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就只能用這個方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這根本不用問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等你醒來後 一切肯定都會變好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不…行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奈威
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別擔心 你會站起來追上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為此所需的力量 已經在你體內萌生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這也太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}追趕上去後會遇到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯又打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要做出那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那些都不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你只要明確自己必須做的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼你總是給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是我在引導你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡的我 是你敞開心房放進去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是你自己在引導自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不被困難的大浪打下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在狂風暴雨的海上勇敢地展翅翱翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你決定好必須做的事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}首先要確認艾利亞斯想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「什麼都別做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}醒來後一切都會變好」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種魔法一般的事 從來都沒發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 帶智世來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她醒著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把我叫做怪物的你 居然做出這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果為自己而棄他人於不顧的我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不也是怪物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救救我 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯說要用我做你的替死鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要把詛咒全部轉嫁到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 離那傢伙遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉 我等等會追上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你先盡可能跑遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也別跟過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是在道什麼歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了想犧牲史黛拉來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想要 想要你和我一起去考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒有跟你保證過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想好了 如果有必要就會用史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你對史黛拉的表情和對我的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很討厭那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就因為這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要你能活下去 我就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到頭來你也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空氣精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會讓你過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愚蠢之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卡達…約瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼 你都知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要對史黛拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來做個交易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}交易？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是你答應
